snippet.title: The Star Named EOS - Official Release Date Trailer | Women Led Games
snippet.description: Get another look at The Star Named EOS, including gameplay and more, from this upcoming story-rich puzzle adventure game built around photography. The Star Named Eos will be available on PC (Steam, Epic Games Store, Humble Store, and GOG), Nintendo Switch, PS5 (PlayStation 5), and Xbox Series X|S on July 23, 2024. Recreate compositions of past photos to uncover the truth of a family mystery. Experience a harmonious mixture of beautiful hand-drawn art and engaging puzzles on a journey of reminiscence.
